Descendants of Pieter Klein (Cline-4)

 

The Cline family tree is one of the largest family trees on the Monroe County, Ohio History and Genealogy websites. As a single family tree it includes 17 generations and numbers about 19,000 entries. Because of its size it is difficult to present the entire family tree as a single file on the website.

To make the presentation of the Cline family tree more manageable, it has been divided into 6-parts. Each part is approximately one-sixth of the whole Pieter Klein family tree. The initial part begins with the ancestor, Pieter Klein, and is identified as Cline-1. Subsequent parts are identified as Cline-2 through Cline-6 and are in consecutive order.
